edu.internet2.middleware.grouper.ui.actions.GrouperCapableAction

  • Packages that use GrouperCapableAction 
    Package Description
    edu.internet2.middleware.grouper.ui.actions
    This package contains all the Struts action classes (referenced in struts-config.xml) which process user inputs and interact with the Grouper API.
